data.description: Multiple Offers!  Best and Final Due Wed Feb. 21st!  Welcome Home to Holiday Village East, Mount Laurel’s sought after 55+ community!  This Strathmore is the largest model with over 2000 sq ft - featuring a two car garage, Sunroom addition with Heat and AC, 2nd floor with 3rd full bathroom, newer Water Heater - 2019, replacement roof - 2016, AC - 2015 and appliances!  The large eat in kitchen has plenty of storage and countertops for the home chef.  The formal dining room and living room feature a gas fireplace with plenty of room to entertain.  Through the glass French doors is the den featuring vaulted ceilings.  The large sunroom has heat and ac making it enjoyable year-round!  The outdoor patio is fenced in and perfect for your BBQ’s.  The bedroom hallway has a storage closet under the staircase and a linen closet for storage.  The primary bedroom features a tray ceiling and a very large walk-in closet plus en-suite bathroom with stall shower.  The main floor guest bedroom, full hall bathroom and laundry room complete this level.  Venture upstairs and you will find the room has a door to keep the utility costs down.  The upper level has a storage closet plus a full bathroom with stall shower and linen closet so it can be used as another guest bedroom or whatever your heart desires!  The two car garage has plenty of shelves for your extra belongings and the outdoors has an underground sprinkler system too!  Holiday Village East has a club house offering a library, card room, craft room, game room and workout room. The outdoor pool is open Memorial Day to Labor Day too! The HOA handles snow removal over 2 inches, lawn mowed and edged, leaf removal, common grounds, outdoor sporting area with tennis and pickle ball plus many daily events! Holiday Village East is close to award winning hospitals, doctors, shopping and restaurants. Come Fall in Love and Make an Offer Today!
